### Start invoice workflow
POST http://localhost:8080/api/workflows/invoice
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "invoice_id": "INV-2025-CLI",
  "pdf_path": "data/sample-invoice.pdf"
}

### Check workflow status
GET http://localhost:8080/api/workflows/INV-2025-CLI
Accept: application/json

### Raise external event (example)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/workflows/childInstanceID/raise-event/event1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "approved": true,
  "comments": "Approved from .http file"
}

### Terminate workflow (cleanup)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/workflows/INV-2025-CLI/terminate
